# UGUI组件指南

Unity UGUI (Unity UI)是Unity的UI系统，用于创建用户界面。以下是主要组件的概览：

## 核心组件

### 可视化组件
- Image: 显示Sprite图像，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/Image.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/Image.cs)
- RawImage: 显示Texture纹理，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/RawImage.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/RawImage.cs)
- Text: 显示文本，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/Text.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/Text.cs)
- Mask: UI遮罩，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/Mask.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/Mask.cs)
- RectMask2D: 高性能矩形遮罩，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/RectMask2D.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/RectMask2D.cs)

### 交互组件
- Button: 按钮，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/Button.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/Button.cs)
- Toggle: 开关/复选框，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/Toggle.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/Toggle.cs)
- Slider: 滑动条，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/Slider.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/Slider.cs)
- Scrollbar: 滚动条，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/Scrollbar.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/Scrollbar.cs)
- Dropdown: 下拉菜单，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/Dropdown.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/Dropdown.cs)
- InputField: 输入框，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/InputField.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/InputField.cs)
- ScrollRect: 滚动视图，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/ScrollRect.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/ScrollRect.cs)

### 布局组件
- LayoutGroup: 布局组基类，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/Layout/LayoutGroup.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/Layout/LayoutGroup.cs)
- HorizontalLayoutGroup: 水平布局，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/Layout/HorizontalLayoutGroup.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/Layout/HorizontalLayoutGroup.cs)
- VerticalLayoutGroup: 垂直布局，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/Layout/VerticalLayoutGroup.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/Layout/VerticalLayoutGroup.cs)
- GridLayoutGroup: 网格布局，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/Layout/GridLayoutGroup.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/Layout/GridLayoutGroup.cs)
- ContentSizeFitter: 内容大小适配，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/Layout/ContentSizeFitter.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/Layout/ContentSizeFitter.cs)

### 其他组件
- Canvas: UI画布，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/Canvas.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/Canvas.cs)
- CanvasGroup: 画布组，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/CanvasGroup.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/CanvasGroup.cs)
- CanvasScaler: 画布缩放器，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/CanvasScaler.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/CanvasScaler.cs)
- GraphicRaycaster: 图形射线检测，位于[Runtime/UI/Core/GraphicRaycaster.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/UI/Core/GraphicRaycaster.cs)

## 事件系统

- EventSystem: 事件系统，位于[Runtime/EventSystem/EventSystem.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/EventSystem/EventSystem.cs)
- EventTrigger: 事件触发器，位于[Runtime/EventSystem/EventTrigger.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/EventSystem/EventTrigger.cs)
- UIBehaviour: UI行为基类，位于[Runtime/EventSystem/UIBehaviour.cs](mdc:Packages/com.unity.ugui/Runtime/EventSystem/UIBehaviour.cs)

